Wait, let me reconsider the spiral more carefully. At the end of ring 22, we have 2025 at position (22, -22). Ring 23 starts:
- 2026 at (23, -22) (move right)
- 2027 at (24, -22) (continue right)
- Then the spiral turns up...

Actually, let me think about this differently. The spiral continues until it needs to turn. From 2025 at (22, -22), ring 23 proceeds:
- Right to x = 23 (that's 2026)
